      "raw_text": "(Scripps News Association.)\n\n\nTELLURIDE, Col, March 2S.-At\nnoon President Mercer of the West\nern Federation of Miners was unable\nto secure bondsmen. He is still a\nprisoner in the county Jail. The\nunionists who own property were\nwilling to become surety but were\nquietly informed that to go on Mer-\nGERS bond would make them persona\nnon grata.\n\n\nThe Federation will probably ar\nrange a cash bond this afternoon.\nSecretary and Treasurer Forbes OF\nthe Telluride union, one of those de-\nported, returned last night and was\narrested. Three other exiles who re-\nturned have been thus far able ia\nelude the military."
    }
